- [ ] Implement STEP 5: Write analysis to REPORT_PATH
- [ ] Implement STEP 6: Emit completion signal (REPORT_CREATED: [path])
- [ ] Add verification checkpoints between steps
- [ ] Follow imperative language standard (MUST/WILL/SHALL)

